govt. employees would be benefited with a cost of Rs. 1098 crore per year.The state govt. of Madhya Pradesh is also going to increase the social security pension amount for elderly from Rs. 300 to Rs. 600 per month (gradually to hike to Rs. 1000). All the citizens from BPL families b/w 60 years to 80 years can avail this pension benefits. This hike in the social security pension amount will incur a burden of Rs. 1300 crore annually on the state exchequer.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}